 25/12/18 Gourdinn Awaken by the strain of our band play Xmas carol . The snow of last night was still lie on the ground in patch but the day turn out finer later on . The day was observ as a close holiday . We are make a good mani new improv round the villag . Our chang of the guard call out a big crowd again today . The peopl at my billet made me a present of a box of sweet sign a card with all their name on it . Went to A B Coy 's dinner which were splendid . All the chap were in great form . I made two speech sign hundr of autograph and then return to my billet . The sound of roister go home gave the street a merri ring . Everyon was in the veri best of good humour tonight .
